76561198129254047,Recommended,224440,31005786,Posted: 7 April,all,elvish123,"If you like building along with tactical defense and RPG this is the game for you. In campaign mode you will need to build palasades ASAP to block raiding spiders. Building a single palasade on the other side of bridges saves resources early on. Then you can stage your heroes by the main spawn outside your village until you have the resources to build a full length fence there. Add a market so you can unlock spider bounties in your research. Now you will have lots of gold for research. Building a blacksmith and researching halberds and xbows will get you the city guards and crosbowmen you need. Stage the crossbow guys on gate house facing a known spider spawn and watch them crank the gold and xp for you. You can add towers to either side of the gatehouse as you see fit. If you get bored of building take out your heroes for adventure and exploring. Research,adventure and building. For me this game is amazing. Even my slower Dell Inspiron 660 with 6gb of ram can handle this game okay. Using the experimental build runs a bit slower and sometimes it sits at 92% for about 1 min then its fine. Cant wait to see what they add next. Marathon gaming sessions may occur so they should add a warning about how addictive this game is LOL :)"
